{"tid":2062432,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］［點睇］十間好食既黃店","createTime":"2020-06-13T06:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:00:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cee0f2cc3c6e5606fd851cb7272dc346e62d807c","tid":2062432,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"港女友 Hong Kong Girlfriend.<br />\n<br />\n雖然黃店不分深黃定淺黃<br />\n但都有分好食同唔好食⋯<br />\n唔好食就唔講啦，想介紹幾間我覺得好好食嘅畀大家！<br />\n好人都deserve食到好東西！<br />\n<br />\n十間我最喜愛的黃店推介：<br />\n（歡迎大家留言反推介番好餐廳！）<br />\n<br />\n1）那個ㄋㄚˋ ㄍㄜ （台式便當）<br />\n呢間我一定要排第一位！！！<br />\n大份夾抵食，仲要好好味！<br />\n便當內每一個配菜我都覺得好食！每次都食哂！<br />\n不過依家搬鋪裝修中，想食就like佢Facebook等開幕詳情<br />\n那個ㄋㄚˋ ㄍㄜ ：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cUZH2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cUZH2U&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=14d7e211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cUZH2U</a><br />\n<br />\n2）越發地道河內料理（越南菜）<br />\n近期我嘅心水，越式法包同撈檬都好好味<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UEWZbH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UEWZbH&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=5a3741d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UEWZbH</a><br />\n<br />\n3）茶芝味（茶飲）<br />\n佢轉手之前我已經有飲開，轉咗手都keep到水準<br />\n芝士奶蓋嚟講，香港我飲過最好飲係呢間<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30zy2SE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30zy2SE&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8afcff6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30zy2SE</a><br />\n<br />\n4）星星 Pho Cha（韓國菜）<br />\n呢間我同麥仔好耐好耐之前已經有食<br />\n韓國菜嚟講呢間我覺得係食過最好食！<br />\n泡菜煎餅係我至愛，水冷麵係麥仔最愛。<br />\n星星 Seng Seng Pho Cha ：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2AYh9qa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2AYh9qa&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a22822da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2AYh9qa</a><br />\n<br />\n5）拉麵台風 （拉麵）<br />\n香港拉麵我最鍾意呢間！佢有三間分店<br />\n我認為荃灣呢間最好食！沾麵拉麵同樣出色<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3fiDtJT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3fiDtJT&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ad22114d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3fiDtJT</a><br />\n<br />\n6）YOLO Cafe （Cafe）<br />\n利申：係朋友嘅屋企人開，不過真心好食<br />\n手工意粉個人認為係必點。<br />\nYOLO Cafe HK ：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30vGAtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30vGAtQ&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=91876c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30vGAtQ</a><br />\n<br />\n7）荳子 Beans（西餐）<br />\n以前同麥仔好鍾意食simplylife<br />\n依家經常都食Beans取代，圓型Waffle好食。<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30BBgVG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30BBgVG&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8780c304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30BBgVG</a><br />\n<br />\n8）Villa Villa（西餐）<br />\nsorly妹仔肚，覺得個免費嘅蒜蓉包好好食<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cYS4se\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cYS4se&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=bb0f4d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cYS4se</a><br />\n<br />\n9）蔥仔越南包（越式法包）<br />\n越式法包推介埋呢間！<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XUAfGF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XUAfGF&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=836a1f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XUAfGF</a><br />\n<br />\n10）普羅旺斯餐廳（法國菜）<br />\n今年生日麥仔帶我去食呢間<br />\n價錢唔平，但真心有驚喜，服務都一流啊。<br />\n特別日子慶祝推介呢間。<br />\n地址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zuf4So\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zuf4So&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=677bcf5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zuf4So</a><br />\n<br />\n繼續大大力支持黃色經濟圈！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkgirlfriend/?refid=52&amp;__tn__=C-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkgirlfriend%2F%3Frefid%3D52%26__tn__%3DC-R&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=517e2d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkgirlfriend/?refid=52&amp;__tn__=C-R</a>"},{"pid":"287c6ba88ae15aa2a120c3068fe1c51643dc1bbb","tid":2062432,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"龍門冰室"},{"pid":"179b40b1ddfab24eb50fb2ed8e63a6c845ad5023","tid":2062432,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"那個幾時開返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}